<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<style>
body{
	font-family:Calibri, Arial; 
	font-size: 11pt;
	width: 100%;
	text-align: left;
    color:rgba(23, 29, 35, 0.74);
    margin: auto;
    padding: 20px
}
td{
    padding-left: 20px !important;
}
.imageClass{
	padding-top:10px;
}
.tdText{
	padding-left: 20px;
}
</style>
	<body>
<div style="text-align: right; padding-right:5px;">
<img src='https://c.na55.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=015f1000001YmRe&oid=00Dj0000001ripe&lastMod=1493805474000'/>
</div>
<br/>
		RE: Affirm Term Loan Number {!Product__c.Name}
		<br><br>
		Outstanding debt of <strong> {!Product__c.Current_Payoff_Amount__c} </strong> due immediately. <span style="color:red; font-style: italic;"> Full amount</span>
		<br><br>
		<span style="margin-bottom:4px;">Dear {!Product__c.First_Name__c},</span>
		<br/><br/>
		According to our records, you have failed to make a payment on your Affirm Term Loan for the above mentioned outstanding debt. Due to not complying with the previous payment requests, we are now considering assigning your account to a collection agency and/or legal action to recover the above amount.
		<br/><br/>
		Immediate payment is now required – contact us immediately at <strong>1-855-266-3131</strong> to make your payment arrangement.
		<br/><br/>
		Failure to make payment will further negatively impact your credit rating with the possibility of being denied future credit.
		<br/><br/><br/>
		<strong>
		Alternatively, you can make your payment using the convenient options listed below:
		</strong>
		<br><br>
		<table style="padding-left:10px; margin-top:4px">
			<tr>
				<td class="imageClass">
					<img src="https://c.na55.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=015f1000001YmPA&oid=00Dj0000001ripe&lastMod=1493803763000" alt="Company Logo" height="40" width="40"/>
				</td>
<td>&nbsp;</td>
				<td class="tdText">Set up a onetime bill payment through your online banking if you bank with BMO, TD, BNS, Credit Unions or Tangerine. Just add Payee: "Affirm Financial". Account number {!LPAD(Product__c.Name, 8, '0')}. Or pay directly at your local bank.</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="imageClass"> <img src="https://c.na55.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=015f1000001YmPC&oid=00Dj0000001ripe&lastMod=1493803763000" alt="Company Logo" height="40" width="40"/>
				</td>
<td>&nbsp;</td>
				<td class="tdText">Contact Affirm Financial to set up a new Pre Authorized withdrawal against your account provided.</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="imageClass"><img src="https://c.na55.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=015f1000001YmP9&oid=00Dj0000001ripe&lastMod=1493803763000" alt="Company Logo" height="40" width="40"/></td>
<td>&nbsp;</td>
				<td class="tdText">Mail a cheque to: Affirm Financial Services, PO Box 53, Station B, London, Ontario, N6A 4V3</td>
			</tr>
		</table>
		<br><br><br>
		Please conduct yourself accordingly.
		<br><br>
		Affirm Financial Services <br>
		1-855-266-3131<br>
		<br><br>
		<div style="font-size: 11px;">
			If your records reflect that you paid this payment prior to the date of this email please contact us so that the discrepancy can be resolved and any necessary corrections made on your account. Please note that payments made using non-guaranteed funds may take up to 7 days for the payment to clear.
		</div>
	</body>
</html>